<li><a href="http://www.hi.is/~eirikur/cases.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.hi.is/~eirikur/cases.pdf" rel="nofollow">The Status of Morphological Case in the Icelandic Lexicon</a> by Eiríkur Rögnvaldsson. Discussion of whether cases convey any inherent syntactic or semantic meaning.</li>
